data.description: 10 ACRES OF COUNTRY LIVING!! PRICED OVER $10K BELOW APPRAISED VALUE!!  Check out this amazing piece of property in Herrick IL offering all main level living with 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths, laundry room, living room, family room, dining room and 2 kitchens. But that's not all! There are 3 outbuildings and a pond! House is ready for your finishing touches to make it your very own peaceful country retreat! Property being offered in the AS IS condition; seller to do no repairs.
